Class StoredCardPostParams

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.payu.india.Payu.PayuUtils

  • public class StoredCardPostParams
extends PaymentDefaultPostParams
    Created by franklin on 6/18/15. To make a Payment using stored credit/debit card user need to call PaymentDefaultPostParams.getPaymentDefaultPostParams() StoredCardPostParams(PaymentDefaultParams, StoredCard) requires PaymentDefaultParams and StoredCard PaymentDefaultParamsincludes the basic payment mandatory default params StoredCard is the user card object you get from card adapter.
